    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-09-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-09-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="454" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d454">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Runyon</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-09-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 11,
                                    1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Statements by gentlemen person ally familiar with Stern case convince
                            Department that he has been most harshly treated. Pardon or commutation
                            being now the only recourse, you will use your utmost efforts to secure
                            remission of sentence of imprisonment.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
